maintext:
It's been less than a month since Donald Trump took office, and the 45th president has already signed a dozen wide-ranging executive orders, hoping to fulfill a number of his campaign promises.
Surrounded by staff during Oval Office photo opportunities, Trump signed the burst of orders within just his first three weeks to undo many of President Barack Obama's regulatory policies.
title: Here's the Full List of Donald Trump's Executive Orders - NBC News
